<br>
1: When you hand the Shimmering Pearl to Zordak Ragefire in Sol B he returns a Swirling Pearl and the Box.<br>
<br>
2: The Warder in Skyfire.  If you possess a Swirling Pearl, she will give you the box.  You can destroy the box, hail her again and get a new one.<br>
<br>
Quest is linear again.  While you can do steps out of order, you still need to do a precise order of hand-ins in order to get to the final battle.<br>
